{"tid":601812,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"任天堂經典「十字掣」回歸！","createTime":"2018-03-22T13:29:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-24T06:09:45.000Z","uid":22675,"like":6,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"4b57cc8644a5180fb6e4edc228499ba1bddd2c25","tid":601812,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T13:29:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/22/212928_a5db9f28b692e27712a59b94094cb7b6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F22%2F212928_a5db9f28b692e27712a59b94094cb7b6.png&h=16eefc94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n任天堂經典「十字掣」回歸！Hori 將在 2018 年 7 月，推出附有「十字按鍵」的 Switch Joy-Con (L)，取代原有獨立四個方向按鍵的設計，售價 2,480 日圓（約 HK$174 / 約 NT$694）。<br />\n<br />\n留意此款任天堂授權的十字型 Switch Joy-Con (L)，只可在「手提模式」下使用，不可當作無線手掣，也不對應 HD 振動、加速及陀螺儀傳感器、手帶、同步、SL 及 SR 按鍵。<br />\n<br />\nHori 官方網站：<br />\n<a href=\"http://hori.jp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhori.jp%2F&d=vmp%2BLbkGsXc7YfaF1kid1PiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=c0fa99a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hori.jp/</a>"},{"pid":"7c02e9d1c6815ee820d5f14d8e391ec172c281b6","tid":601812,"uid":99700,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T13:33:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img4.cache.netease.com/photo/0031/2017-01-27/CBQ5RVT771570031.550x.0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg4.cache.netease.com%2Fphoto%2F0031%2F2017-01-27%2FCBQ5RVT771570031.550x.0.jpg&h=82a8dd4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我要呢個"},{"pid":"7f613073ab52e007a157d1f1270f0d2052b8bcd9","tid":601812,"uid":2772,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T13:35:00.000Z","msg":"仲以為係紅白機果款<br />\n有碌棍係十字中間棟上黎"},{"pid":"500ca7a58ad44e542e829f1b96886bbfd5159864","tid":601812,"uid":1972,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T13:37:09.000Z","msg":"整個joycon版嘅 pro con咪得囉"},{"pid":"70d2b03933d6aae266a50f5e6e74563e7d4af818","tid